%% Data Flow Diagram - llama-stack-provider-ragas
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as RagasEvaluatorInline<br/>(in-process)
    participant Inference as Inference Backend<br/>(Ollama/vLLM)
    participant Remote as RagasEvaluatorRemote<br/>(in-process)
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pods
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation

    Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>8321/TCP HTTP plaintext
    LLS->>Inline: run_eval() (Python API)
    Inline->>LLS: DatasetIO API (in-process)<br/>Retrieve dataset
    Inline->>LLS: Inference API (in-process)<br/>LLM + Embeddings
    LLS->>Inference: HTTP 11434/TCP<br/>API token (optional)
    Inference-->>LLS: Model response
    LLS-->>Inline: Inference result
    Note over Inline: Run Ragas metrics:<br/>answer_relevancy, context_precision,<br/>faithfulness, context_recall
    Inline-->>LLS: Evaluation results
    LLS-->>Client: job_result response<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)

    Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>8321/TCP HTTP plaintext
    LLS->>Remote: run_eval() (Python API)
    Remote->>KFP: GET /healthz<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Remote: Health OK
    Remote->>KFP: POST /runs (create pipeline run)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Remote: Run ID

    Note over KFP, S3: Async Pipeline Execution
    KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule retrieve_data step
    KFPPod->>LLS: GET /datasets/*<br/>8321/TCP HTTP plaintext
    LLS-->>KFPPod: Dataset (JSONL)
    KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule run_ragas step
    KFPPod->>LLS: POST /inference/*<br/>8321/TCP HTTP plaintext
    LLS->>Inference: Forward inference request
    Inference-->>LLS: Model response
    LLS-->>KFPPod: Inference result
    KFPPod->>S3: PUT results<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>KFPPod: OK

    Client->>LLS: POST /eval/job_status
    LLS->>Remote: job_status()
    Remote->>KFP: GET /runs/{id}<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Remote: Run status
    Remote-->>LLS: Status
    LLS-->>Client: Job status

    Client->>LLS: POST /eval/job_result
    LLS->>Remote: job_result()
    Remote->>S3: GET results<br/>443/TCP HTTPS AWS IAM
    S3-->>Remote: Evaluation results
    Remote-->>LLS: Results
    LLS-->>Client: Evaluation results
